comments.content:
Hi Dara,

‘Jeffries’ is similar to/probably based on [Trade Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20080415140039/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/trade-gothic/familytree.html).  
Not sure about the other one. In [this older thread](http://web.archive.org/web/20080415140039/http:/www.typophile.com/node/6332), a typeface named [New Age](http://web.archive.org/web/20080415140039/http:/www.identifont.com/show?7BF) is mentioned – however, it seems to be unavailable now.
